# 🚀 Developer Portfolio

A modern and responsive portfolio website built to showcase my skills, projects, and work as a developer.

---

## 🔥 About the Project

This portfolio is designed to represent my journey as a developer. It highlights my technical skills, projects, and ability to build clean, interactive, and user-friendly interfaces.

The main focus of this project is:
- Clean UI/UX
- Smooth animations
- Structured and scalable code
- Performance optimization

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- React.js
- Framer Motion (for animations)

---

## ✨ Features

- Responsive design (works on mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Smooth page transitions and animations
- Interactive UI components
- Organized project showcase section
- Easy navigation

